<figureCitation box="[680,794,1996,2021]" captionStart="FIGURE 19" captionStartId="45.[151,249,1978,2000]" captionTargetBox="[412,1170,193,1955]" captionTargetId="figure@45.[412,1175,193,1956]" captionTargetPageId="45" captionText="FIGURE 19. Photograph of Pogonomyrmex cunicularius Mayr ergatoid queen: (A) frontal view of head, (B) lateral view of body, and (C) dorsal view of body (CASENT 0173109). Photographs by April Nobile from www. AntWeb. org." pageId="46" pageNumber="47">
